prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style watercolor illustration of a distinguished, elderly tortoise wearing a tiny, festive party hat, looking slightly bewildered as it slowly pushes a single, large, brightly colored birthday balloon with its nose. The tortoise has a comically serious expression. The background is a soft, minimalist wash of pastel colors with subtle paint splatters and visible paper texture. Centered on the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Don't worry, age is just a number... a really, really high, un-fun number." The overall style is flat 2D, with artistic brush strokes and organic paint bleeds, perfect for printing.
